name: Hot Tub, Pool Table, Ping Pong & Poker: Big Sky
body_description:
Discover Big Sky, a luxurious ski-in/ski-out mountain retreat with a rich rental history and breathtaking panoramic views near Deep Creek Lake and the surrounding peaks.

Unwind in our spacious hot tub or warm up by the grand stone fireplace. The fun never ends inside - challenge your crew to pool, poker, ping pong, or shuffleboard in our fully equipped game rooms.

Whether you're hitting the slopes at Wisp Resort or by the lake, this spacious year-round resort offers the perfect adventure!


THE SPACE

Soak in sweeping panoramic mountain views as you grill on the back deck of Big Sky, a stunning vacation home perched high atop Marsh Mountain in the Highline Community of Deep Creek Lake.

Blending luxury with a cozy Rocky Mountain ambiance, Big Sky offers year-round adventure and relaxation. Just steps from Wisp Resort, you’ll have easy access to skiing, snowboarding, golfing, mountain biking, and spa services. The Adventure Sports Center International and its world-renowned whitewater rafting course are also within walking distance.

After a day of adventure, retreat to the spacious, heated garage for a friendly game of ping pong or cornhole, or unwind in one of the three private master suites. Challenge your group to a pool or shuffleboard in the loft or relax in one of the two living areas. With five bedrooms, a well-appointed kitchen, and thoughtful amenities throughout, it is perfect for multi-family getaways or group vacations.

This casita is unique and inviting, and it has everything you need for a relaxing vacation. Whether you're looking to explore the city or just relax in the hot tub, this casita is the perfect place to stay.

Guests will have access to the entire home during their stay, except for the owner's closets and storage areas, which are locked.
